---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Tours Cinematográficos - Franpisco Adventure"
	description="Revisa el increíble catálogo de asaltos montañeros visual a nevados colosales en el majestuoso ande suramericano."
>
	<section class="cinematic-section tours-hero-bg">
		<div class="watermark-text" style="top:25%;">TREKKING</div>
		
		<div class="glass-container">
			<div class="section-header-epic center-epic">
				<h1 class="epic-title">RUTAS Y<br/><span class="text-accent">CONQUISTAS</span></h1>
				<div class="laser-divider center"></div>
				<p class="epic-subtitle">Elige en tu destino el temible asalto y batifondo que desafiará a tu ser y espíritu vivo terrenal.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="posters-grid">
				<!-- Poster 1: Inca -->
				<article class="epic-poster tour-inca">
					<div class="poster-overlay">
                        <div class="poster-badges">
                            <span class="p-badge b-gold">Ruta Ancestral Fuerte</span>
                            <span class="p-badge b-green">4 DÍAS MÁGICA - INTERMEDIO FÍSICO</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="poster-text">
                            <h3>Camino Inca Clásico a la Ciudadela</h3>
                            <p>Trekking enigmático y sagrado. 4 impresionantes días de caminata mágica sudamericana sobre rocas incas puras y húmedo y crudo bosque peruano nuboso y nativo.</p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-epic">Solicitar Gran Invasión ➔</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
				</article>

				<!-- Poster 2: QD -->
				<article class="epic-poster tour-qo">
					<div class="poster-overlay">
                        <div class="poster-badges">
                            <span class="p-badge b-blue">Ruinas Fantasmas Vírgenes Perdidas</span>
                            <span class="p-badge b-green">1 A 2 DÍAS LIGEROS MAGICOS - BAJA</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="poster-text">
                            <h3>Línea Magisterial Secreta a Huchuy Qosqo</h3>
                            <p>El silencio prístino de Sudamérica antigua. Senderos olvidados ricos e indomablemente secretos cruzando montañas rocosas vacías prístinas rumbo a santuarios gigantes incas limpios perdidos.</p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-epic">Explorar el Sendero ➔</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
				</article>

                <!-- Poster 3: Ice -->
				<article class="epic-poster tour-ice">
					<div class="poster-overlay">
                        <div class="poster-badges">
                            <span class="p-badge b-ice">Letal Frio Andino Peruano</span>
                            <span class="p-badge b-red">Glacial Alto (5,200 msnm)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="poster-text">
                            <h3>Asedio al Macizo Fuerte Pastoruri</h3>
                            <p>Aventura técnica indomable a 5mil en la inmaculada brutal gigante Cordillera Blanca Peruana nevada. Exigencia altísima letal viva y un increíble cara a cara monumental gélido helado andino sagrado duro puro con los hielos mágicos puros sagrados sur de vida y muerte.</p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-epic">Enlistar Supervivencia ➔</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
				</article>

                <!-- Poster 4: Brutal -->
				<article class="epic-poster tour-epic">
					<div class="poster-overlay">
                        <div class="poster-badges">
                            <span class="p-badge b-blood">Gigantesca Épica Total Colosal (Top 3)</span>
                            <span class="p-badge b-black">SUPERVIVENCIA DURA ROTUNDA 100%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="poster-text">
                            <h3>Circuito Supremo Máster Total Fuerte: Huayhuash</h3>
                            <p>Basta rudeza majestuosidad brutal inquebrantable indomable letal del fin. Entre 8 a increíbles puros 13 duros letales grandes crudos de aislamiento extremo, picos majestuosos infinitos gélidos mortales puros fríos duros.</p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-epic">Someter Máximo Reto ➔</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* CINEMATIC BASE STYLES */
	.cinematic-section {
		position: relative;
		min-height: calc(100vh - 80px); /* Ocupa hasta abajo del navbar */
		overflow: hidden;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		padding: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 6rem) clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	/* Gradiente de Montaña de Noche */
	.tours-hero-bg {
		background: #06090f; /* Negro Abismo */
		background-image: 
			radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%),
			radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);
	}

	.watermark-text {
		position: absolute;
		top: 30%;
		left: 10%;
		font-size: clamp(10rem, 30vw, 30rem);
		font-weight: 900;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
		letter-spacing: -5px;
		z-index: 1;
		pointer-events: none;
		line-height: 1;
		white-space: nowrap;
		user-select: none;
	}

	.glass-container {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 5;
		max-width: 1600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.section-header-epic.center-epic {
		text-align: center;
		margin: 0 auto clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) auto;
		max-width: 900px;
	}

	.epic-title {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
		font-weight: 900;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.05;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: -1px;
		color: #e2e8f0;
	}

	.text-accent {
		color: #38bdf8;
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
	}

	.laser-divider.center { 
		height: 3px;
        margin: 1.5rem auto; 
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #38bdf8, transparent); 
        width: clamp(100px, 20vw, 250px); 
    }

	.epic-subtitle {
		font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);
		color: #94a3b8;
		font-weight: 300;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
        line-height: 1.6;
	}

	/* CINEMATIC POSTERS GRID */
	.posters-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 350px), 1fr));
		gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
	}

	.epic-poster {
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		min-height: 450px; /* Poster vertical alto de Película */
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		background: #1e293b; /* Fallback incase */
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
		transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1), box-shadow 0.5s ease;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

    /* Simulando Imágenes de Background con CSS Oscuro Poderoso y Degradados de Color */
    .tour-inca { background: linear-gradient(0deg, #18231c 0%, rgba(30, 41, 59, 1) 100%); } /* Tono Musgo/Ruina */
    .tour-qo { background: linear-gradient(0deg, #171c26 0%, rgba(20, 30, 40, 1) 100%); }   /* Tono Noche Piedra */
    .tour-ice { background: linear-gradient(0deg, #112738 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 1) 100%); }  /* Tono Hielo Profundo */
    .tour-epic { background: linear-gradient(0deg, #2a0b12 0%, #0c0812 100%); }             /* Tono Aleta Sangre Extrema Top3 */

	.epic-poster:hover {
		transform: translateY(-15px) scale(1.02);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
	}

	.poster-overlay {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		width: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.95) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.4) 60%, transparent 100%);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: flex-end;
        height: 100%;
	}

	.poster-badges {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 10px;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.p-badge {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		padding: 6px 14px;
		border-radius: 4px; /* Cuadriculado Duro Película */
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
	}

    /* Badges de Lujo */
    .b-gold { background: rgba(202, 138, 4, 0.2); color: #fcd34d; border: 1px solid rgba(252, 211, 77, 0.3); }
    .b-green { background: rgba(21, 128, 61, 0.2); color: #86efac; border: 1px solid rgba(134, 239, 172, 0.3); }
    .b-blue { background: rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);  color: #93c5fd; border: 1px solid rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.3); }
    .b-gray { background: rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.3); color: #cbd5e1; border: 1px solid rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.3); }
    .b-ice { background: rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.2); color: #7dd3fc; border: 1px solid rgba(125, 211, 252, 0.3); text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(125,211,252, 0.5);}
    .b-red { background: rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.2); color: #fca5a5; border: 1px solid rgba(252, 165, 165, 0.3); }
    .b-blood { background: rgba(153, 27, 27, 0.5); color: #fecaca; border: 1px solid #ef4444; }
    .b-black { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); color: #ef4444; border: 1px solid #7f1d1d; }

	.poster-text h3 {
		color: #ffffff;
		font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.1;
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
	}

	.poster-text p {
		color: #94a3b8;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
	}

	.btn-epic {
		display: inline-block;
		color: #38bdf8;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-decoration: none;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.epic-poster:hover .btn-epic {
		color: #ffffff;
		transform: translateX(10px);
	}
</style>
